name: THIS PLACE
description:
What I picture in my head every time I listen to “This Place” by Saxon Shore. 

A transformative take on a photo by Indro Muktiono through an improvised generative art technique and multi-layered motion to add depth and parallax effects.  

Find me on Twitter & Instagram: @indiedo

Jakarta, November 16, 2021.
 3840 × 2112 seamlessly looping MP4.
